attributionInfo.brokerName: Century 21 Carolyn Riley RL. Est. Srvcs, Inc.

data.description: This home offers great affordability in the City of Green and close to everything in the Portage Lakes! Huge updated and fully applianced kitchen features plenty of cabinets, a moveable island, and a breakfast bar that leads into the Dining/Great room area. There is a first floor bedroom and two large bedrooms upstairs (one is tandem). The basement has a finished rec room and also a unique finished "crawl" area (not included in the lower square footage) that will be a favorite place for the kids! The garage is almost large enough for two cars and will be good for storage or possibly a future work shop. The well and septic have been regularly maintained and updated as needed.
